{
  "texts": [
    "We stratify this splitting across political bias, to ensure each political bias is represented equally in both the train and test sets.",
    "Political Bias.",
    "Separate from editorial bias, publishers tend to exhibit a political bias as well.",
    "MBFC has annotated all publishers on a left-right political bias continuum.",
    "We map all 'Extreme Left' and 'Left' publishers to a coarser 'Left' group, and vice versa for the 'Right'-side of the political spectrum."
  ]
}